  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Tom</b> is a given name in Westeros. Characters named Tom include:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Spotted_Tom\" title=\"Spotted Tom\">Spotted Tom</a>, a member of the Band of Nine</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tom_of_Sevenstreams\" title=\"Tom of Sevenstreams\">Tom of Sevenstreams</a>, a singer and outlaw</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tom_the_Strummer\" title=\"Tom the Strummer\">Tom the Strummer</a>, a knight and singer</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tom_Barleycorn\" title=\"Tom Barleycorn\">Tom Barleycorn</a>, a ranger of the Night's Watch</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tom_Codd\" title=\"Tom Codd\">Tom Codd</a>, an ironborn captain</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tom_Costayne\" title=\"Tom Costayne\">Tom Costayne</a>, a member of the Kingsguard</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tom_Flowers\" title=\"Tom Flowers\">Tom Flowers</a>, a bastard of House Caswell</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tom_Tanglebeard\" title=\"Tom Tanglebeard\">Tom Tanglebeard</a>, a man of Dragonstone</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tom_Tangletongue\" title=\"Tom Tangletongue\">Tom Tangletongue</a>, a man of Dragonstone</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tom_Tidewood\" title=\"Tom Tidewood\">Tom Tidewood</a>, an ironborn sailor</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tom_Turnip\" title=\"Tom Turnip\">Tom Turnip</a>, a court fool</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tomard\" title=\"Tomard\">Tomard</a>, a Winterfell guard known as Fat Tom</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tommard_Heddle\" title=\"Tommard Heddle\">Tommard Heddle</a>, a rivermen knight</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/TomToo\" title=\"TomToo\">TomToo</a>, Tomard's son</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tom&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span